  - src/ledger/ledger.ts
      journal.jsonl append/load shape, torn-line tolerance, and the
      canonical (sort-deep) JSON hashing helper are adapted from
      omegacode src/runtime/journal.ts and src/runtime/keys.ts.
      Deliberately left behind: the v3 chained call-tree key lineage
      (branch keys, fan-out counters) and the determinism lint — under
      loop-as-data the resume key collapses to hash(stepId + inputs).

  - src/kernel/types.ts
      The Executor protocol is a rename of omegacode's
      Worker.runAgent(spec, ctx) -> AgentResult seam
      (src/worker/index.ts), generalized beyond LLM providers.
      Deliberately left behind: the node:vm sandbox trunk
      (src/runtime/sandbox.ts, primitives.ts) — workflow-as-untrusted-code
      is the trust model this kernel rejects.

